			<p>(<a href="docs/current/whats_new.html">Changes</a>)</p>
			<br/>
			
			<p><a href="download/agree.shtml?terrier-3.0.tar.gz"><img border="0" src="img/downloadicon-transparent-10pc.png"><strong>terrier-3.0.tar.gz</strong></a></p>
			<br/>
