<div class="wrapper col4">
  <div id="services">
    <ul>
      <li>        
        <div class="fl_left">
          <h3>Learn More</h3>
          <p>Terrier has extensive documentation about <a href="./docs/current/configure_indexing.html">indexing</a> and <a href="./docs/current/configure_retrieval.html">retrieval</a>, as well as about <a href="docs/current/">running experiments</a> using TREC test collections.</p>
		 
        </div>
      </li>
      <li>
        <div class="fl_right">
          <h3>Ask</h3>
          <p>Join the active community <a href="./http://terrier.org/forum//">forum</a> to ask for help with any part of Terrier, or update the <a href="http://ir.dcs.gla.ac.uk/wiki/Terrier">wiki</a>.</p>
			
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="last">
        <div class="fl_right">
          <h3>Contribute</h3>
          <p>Found a bug, or want to improve Terrier? You can <a href="http://ir.dcs.gla.ac.uk/wiki/Terrier/Contribute">contribute</a> to Terrier, by filing issues on the <a href="./issues/">issue tracker</a>.
        </div>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <br class="clear" />
